8139BA2188CC2D95D012678D6C78CA4C6217A20F.query: CREATE TABLE "users" ('id' INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, 'email' VARCHAR NOT NULL CHECK (length('email') <= 255), 'username' VARCHAR NOT NULL CHECK (length('username') <= 255), 'bio' VARCHAR NOT NULL CHECK (length('bio') <= 255), 'image' VARCHAR NOT NULL CHECK (length('image') <= 255));
